OL,3,CSuspect found asleep in child-sized
OL,4,Cbed arrested on suspicion of burglary
OL,6,FWatch the moment police arrest a
OL,7,Fsuspect found asleep in a child-sized
OL,8,Fbed.
OL,10,FPolice have released footage of the
OL,11,Fmoment a burglary suspect was
OL,12,Farrested, after being found asleep in
OL,13,Fa small bed at a house in
OL,14,FNottinghamshire.
OL,16,FOfficers were called to a house in
OL,17,FNewark, after getting reports that it
OL,18,Fwas being burgled.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
